Desc: Closet for changing clothes...er, equipment.

Name: Landscape
Desc: Beautiful landscape painting.

Name: Dark Leather Sofa

Name: Wall Lamp
Desc: Glows with a warm, gentle yellow light.

Name: Patio Window
Desc: Sit by the window side and enjoy the view.

Name: Menu Board
Desc: The cafe's menu is written in rather distinctive handwriting.

Name: Round Table
Desc: Romantic round table for two.

Name: Potted Plant
Desc: Not sure what kind of plant it is.

Name: Storage Rack
Desc: The storage rack looks a little bare. A few accessories might endear it to customers more.

Name: Long Table
Desc: Simple long table with white tablecloth.

Name: Tall Chair
Desc: Simple yet elegant tall chair

Name: Coffee Table
Desc: Common coffee table, with a quaint little flower.

Name: Table Set
Desc: What better way to discuss business than to do it over a cup of coffee?

Name: Cafe Floor
Desc: Light-blue floor for the cafe.

Name: Cafe Ceiling
Desc: Ceiling with a little light hanging from it.

Name: Cafe Wall
Desc: Simple cafe wall.

Name: Locker
Desc: Stark metal lockers.

Name: Fluorescent Light
Desc: Looks like it has been in use for a long time...

Name: Office Desk
Desc: Pick up after yourself, you slob!

Name: Blinds
Desc: Blinds that lets rows of sunlight through.

Name: Box of Parts
Desc: Holds various equipment parts. Looks heavy.

Name: Vending Machine
Desc: No need to insert money - just give it a good ol' kick!

Name: Control Terminal
Desc: Control terminal for the room. Give it a nice hard slap if sparks start flying from it.

Name: Messy Storage Rack
Desc: No one wants to tidy up the mess.

Name: Toilet
Desc: Nice and clean. No need to worry about the smell.

Name: Worktable
Desc: For working on malfunctioning parts.

Name: Bar Stool
Desc: Old bar stool. Don't break it.

Name: Bar Counter
Desc: A beautiful bartender will give this bar counter a brand new look.

Name: Cloth Sofa
Desc: Clean and tidy comes first, comfort second.

Name: Sofa Set
Desc: Connect them to seat even more people.

Name: Poster α
Desc: Poster of a Construct. Not sure why it is from the side.

Name: Poster β
Desc: A poster of Liv.

Name: Poster γ
Desc: A photo of Lucia realizing that the Commandant is taking a photo of her.

Name: Neon Logo
Desc: Neon sign of Gray Raven.

Name: Rack
Desc: A curious storage rack. The top shelf seems to be locked.

Name: Punk Floor
Desc: Floor blocks in punk style.

Name: Punk Ceiling
Desc: Ceiling with exposed metal frame.

Name: Punk Logo Wall
Desc: Very distinctive wall.

Name: Paper Window
Desc: Japanese paper window over a wooden frame. Do not poke it.

Name: Cushion Chair
Desc: Chair with cushioned back.

Name: Potted Bamboo
Desc: Bamboo in a bot, giving the room a sense of elegance.

Name: Sakura Fan
Desc: Wall decoration with cherry blossom print.

Name: Hanging Painting
Desc: Said to be a famous painting, but only part of it remains.

Name: Japanese Shelf
Desc: Elegant shelf with paper windows.

Name: Futon
Desc: Don't catch a cold.

Name: Sakura Screen
Desc: Elegant and discreet, a unique picture of culture.

Name: Katana Stand
Desc: For displaying katanas. Lucia's favorite.

Name: Kotatsu
Desc: Once you go in, you can never get out.

Name: Drinking Table
Desc: There is nothing like a stiff drink and some nice salty snacks after work.

Name: Wooden Tub
Desc: Warm vapors rise from this wooden bathtub. Even Constructs need to keep themselves clean.

Name: Japanese Lantern
Desc: Traditional paper lantern, like the ones that guide the dead into the underworld.

Name: Japanese Floor
Desc: Warm and gentle wooden floor.

Name: Beam Ceiling
Desc: Beam ceiling in traditional style, like the one in izakayas.

Name: Sakura Wall
Desc: Cherry-pink wall. One can almost smell the sweet scent of cherry blossoms.

Name: Cyber Egg
Desc: Futuristic holo-projector, displaying various text and images when switched on.

Name: Retro Floor Lamp
Desc: Minimalist floor lamp in retro style. The outstanding workmanship is apparent upon close inspection.

Name: Double Bed
Desc: Classic double bed made from fine red oak. Very comfortable, but the color of the linens is questionable.

Name: Mistletoe Wreath
Desc: Wreath made from mistletoe, celebrating the Christmas season.

Name: Christmas Gift Pile
Desc: Unopened Christmas gifts. Keep an eye on thieves!

Name: Nightstand
Desc: Classic nightstand with candlestick, books and photo frame.

Name: European Closet
Desc: Large European closet made from red oak. Noble and dignified.

Name: Wall Chandelier
Desc: Wall chandelier with twin candles, bright and warm.

Name: Wall Clock
Desc: Announces the time firmly and reliably. A gentleman's piece.

Name: Fireplace
Desc: Fireplace made from red oak and copper, warming both body and heart.

Name: Lattice Window With Curtain
Desc: The red curtain gives this unremarkable window a remarkable elegance.

Name: Christmas Tree
Desc: A must for Christmas season, with Christmas stockings and tiny bells hanging from it. A sight to behold when lit.

Name: European Sofa
Desc: Minimalist sofa without excessive ornamentation, and is all the more comfortable for it.

Name: Dawn (Oil on Canvas)
Desc: Oil painting titled "Dawn". The rays of the rising sun are depicted with broad, bold brush strokes.

Name: European Bookshelf
Desc: Medium-sized retro bookshelf, with an eye-catching arch design.

Name: Christmas Table
Desc: Red tablecloth on wooden table, complete with turkey and candlesticks.

Name: European Chair
Desc: Minimalist red oak chair with high back. A good manners test.

Name: Cushion Stool
Desc: Short stool with leather cushion. Great for the bedroom, not so much for the guest room.

Name: Tile Floor
Desc: Dark tile floor with a wave pattern that prevents slipping.

Name: Christmas Wall
Desc: Decorated with mistletoe, bells and ribbons. There is even a tiny fireplace built into the wall.

Name: Chandelier Beam
Desc: Classy wooden beam adorned with chandelier, lightning up even the largest rooms.

Name: Floating Kuroro
Desc: Kuroro floats above a bonsai. Is it a model or the real thing?

Name: Trash Cans
Desc: Waste separation is crucial to keep the base's intricate recycling system running at max efficiency.

Name: Triple Toilet
Desc: The result of cutting-edge research across many different fields. The perfect industrial design is intended to help Constructs establish bonds with each other and become comfortable with communal life.

Name: Recharge Station
Desc: Allows for quick recharging of Constructs and vehicles. Despite the high endurance of fusion batteries, it never hurts to have a backup plan.

Name: Camera
Desc: High-performance camera that can record high-definition videos. It can be used on a tripod or handheld.

Name: Motorcycle
Desc: Standard one-seater bike that Constructs use to navigate the vast wasteland, moving from stronghold to stronghold.

Name: Divider
Desc: Want a private space? Order the newly-launched divider!

Name: Lantern Pole
Desc: A pole that has small lanterns hanging on it. Remember not to let Nanami take any one of them.

Name: Chinese Tea Table
Desc: One pot of tea, two lots of dim sum, and a few friends playing chess with you. These are all you need to enjoy your time.

Name: Chinese Armchair
Desc: Although it is very hard, its regular shape can help prevent back pain.

Name: Chinese Desk
Desc: A desk with Four Treasures of the Study on it. Wonder whose work desk is it.

Name: Chinese Bench
Desc: A quaint bench that would be uncomfortable if you don't sit up straight.

Name: Chinese Chest of Drawers
Desc: A big drawer that seems to hold everything you buy in a whole year.

Name: Chinese Cupboard
Desc: A small cabinet with a shelf. Tea leaves, teapots, tea cups and small charcoal stoves can be stored in it.

Name: Earthenware Jar
Desc: An empty jar. Everyone knows drinking is forbidden in the dormitory.

Name: Chinese Plant Stand
Desc: A pear wood plant stand made by a well-known craftsman in the Golden Age. The colored glass bottle placed on it is rumored to be a counterfeit made by 3D printing.

Name: Spring Couplet
Desc: A handwritten spring couplet, one of the few traditions that has survived from the Golden Age to this day.

Name: Teahouse's Flag
Desc: A linen cloth with some ancient words written on it. Would anyone come after hanging this up?

Name: Teahouse's Window Pane
Desc: A Chinese-style window pane, but even though you open it, all you can see is the dormitory's metal walls.

Name: Teahouse's Counter
Desc: A long desk and a good hiding spot when playing hide-and-seek.

Name: Chinese Floor Lamp
Desc: A traditional floor lamp made of wood and rice paper, but the bulb is nuclear.

Name: Chinese Screen
Desc: A screen that depicts people's daily life in a market long before the Golden Age. You will expose your feet when hiding behind it.

Name: Chinese Bed
Desc: A traditional soft bed installed with temperature control system and wireless network, making you never want to leave.

Name: Teahouse's Door
Desc: A traditional door that makes you feel you're stepping into a teahouse.

Name: Hanging Lantern
Desc: A large lantern hung high from the ceiling, filling the whole room with festive atmosphere.

Name: Chinese Carpet
Desc: A traditional carpet. Don't step on it with shoes on!

Name: Church Dome
Desc: A baby blue church dome. The light from the dome is warm and comfortable.

Name: Church Floor
Desc: Those square tiles are Bianca's favorite flooring style.

Name: Church Wall
Desc: A clean, baby blue church wall.

Name: Church Pew
Desc: A wooden pew with a delicate fragrance.

Name: Holy Coffin
Desc: It feels sacred to sleep on it. It can produce dim light to help the user calm the mind. Much softer than it looks.

Name: Church Niche
Desc: A little idol is covered with a book someone left in the niche.

Name: Church Chair
Desc: A single-seater church chair that smells of a mild fragrance.

Name: Church Piano Bench
Desc: A little piano bench tailor-made for the piano. It feels cold when sitting on it.

Name: Church Pulpit
Desc: A church book with many sticky notes lies on the pulpit.

Name: Globe
Desc: Nanami loves to put her finger through the semi-transparent projection globe.

Name: Holy Cross
Desc: A silver cross with a blue ribbon. Church members will pray before it.

Name: Church Piano
Desc: A well-preserved, valuable piano.

Name: Church Fence
Desc: An exquisite white marble fence that is sleek to the touch.

Name: Church Flower Bed
Desc: A flower bed planted with forget-me-nots. It imbues the room with moderate fragrance.

Name: Stained Glass Window
Desc: The stained glass brings more sunlight into the room.

Name: Painting of Snow
Desc: A painting of Father Snow created by Bianca.

Name: Holy Banner
Desc: A light blue banner with a church logo.

Name: Church Secret Wall
Desc: A secret wall that glows dimly. Nobody knows how to open it.

Name: Kowloong Banner
Desc: A banner in the entertainment cabin of the Nighter that shows hospitality towards every guest.

Name: Chessboard Floor
Desc: The entertainment cabin's multifunctional floor. It can be used for a game in addition to providing the guests with various services.

Name: Kowloong Cabin Wall
Desc: The cabin wall of the Nighter's entertaining cabin with a huge Kowloong icon.

Name: Kowloong Bench
Desc: The prototype of this bench is untraceable due to its extremely long history. The number on it appears to have a special meaning.

Name: Kowloong Folding Bed
Desc: A folding bed created for space-saving purposes. Pressing the buttons on both sides can transform it into a real bed.

Name: Kowloong Rack
Desc: The antiques are attached to the shelf, so they will never fall off even if the shelf is moved around.

Name: Kowloong Cauldron
Desc: The cauldron's core is both heating and filtering the water within, preparing it for drinking, cooking, and bathing.

Desc: A piece that originally represented a "soldier". It has been reshaped and given a representation of the "royal guard" at Nanami's hands.

Name: Chess - Pawn (Black)
Desc: A piece that originally represented a "pawn". It has been reshaped and given a representation of the "royal guard" at Nanami's hands.

Name: Chess - General (Black)

Desc: A piece that originally represented a "horse". It has been reshaped and given a representation of the "knight" at Nanami's hands.

Desc: A piece that originally represented a "cannon". It has been reshaped by Nanami.

Desc: A piece that originally represented a "marshal". It has been reshaped and given a representation of the "king" at Nanami's hands.

Desc: A piece that originally represented a "minister". It has been reshaped and given a representation of the "bishop" at Nanami's hands.

Desc: A piece that originally represented a "horse". It has been reshaped and given a representation of the "knight" at Nanami's hands.

Desc: A piece that originally represented an "advisor". It has been reshaped and given a representation of the "queen" at Nanami's hands.

Name: Chess - Chariot (Red)
Desc: A piece that originally represented a "chariot". It has been reshaped and given a representation of the "rook" at Nanami's hands.

Name: Kowloong Round Window
Desc: A window of the Nighter . It is not made of paper. Please do not poke it.

Name: Trading Panel
Desc: A trading panel in the entertainment cabin of the Nighter. It displays real-time trading and match information in the cabin.

Name: Shallow Fish Tank
Desc: A huge fish tank that is installed with a water recirculating system at the bottom. You can even plunge into it and swim for a while.

Name: Island Beam
Desc: Multiple fans dispel the scorching heat on the island.

Name: Island Floor
Desc: A floor that can cool down the room with its special material on the surface. However, it is extremely slippery. Never try to slide on it with slippers!

Name: Coastal Wooden Wall
Desc: A wall made of 100% wood. It fills the air with a refreshing sweet fragrance.

Name: Coastal Wine Cabinet
Desc: Different wines are placed on this wooden cabinet. Nanami and Sophia are prohibited from touching it.

Name: Island Entertainment Table
Desc: An islander's table recreated by the WGAA, coming with a popular board game on the island.

Name: Island Patio Window
Desc: A big patio window that displays a blue sky and clear sea water.

Name: Island Window
Desc: Liv has planted some flowers on the windowsill. You can enjoy a gentle fragrance even when the window is closed.

Name: Island Long Table
Desc: An islander's long table recreated by the WGAA, coming with a set of billiard balls.

Name: Island Sofa
Desc: A comfy shell-shaped sofa. Once you sit in it, you will fall asleep without even noticing it.

Name: Island Mural
Desc: A mural depicting an ocean scene. Who is the painter of it?

Name: Island Swim Ring
Desc: A swim ring with multiple decorations. Can it still float in water?

Name: Island Chair
Desc: An islander's chair recreated by the WGAA. Nothing to write home about.

Name: Island Wall Lamp
Desc: An energy-saving, exquisite lamp that glows warmly on summer nights.

Name: Coastal Bed
Desc: A boat bed with a light smell of sea water.

Name: Snow Grill
Desc: The sizzling grill smells great.

Name: Winter Ceiling
Desc: The pure white ceiling is covered in frost and snow.

Name: Snow Floor
Desc: Made from different types of timber, the floor has a snow pattern.

Name: Winter Wall
Desc: This solid stone wall has a heat insulating layer inside.

Name: Winter Shelf
Desc: The blue shelf looks like it's carved from ice.

Name: Winter Desk
Desc: A flat rectangle desk with documents stacked on top.

Name: Winter Window
Desc: Always covered in snow.

Name: Icy Impressions
Desc: This artwork is signed by the abstract artist SA-1 himself.

Name: Snow Table
Desc: The warm drink on the table can drive the winter chill away.

Name: Snow Sofa
Desc: There are blankets and pillows on the sofa.

Name: Snowy Night Cabinet
Desc: This bed cabinet has a night lamp on top.

Name: Snow Folding Chair
Desc: A convenient folding chair with snowy pattern.

Name: Winter Wall Lamp
Desc: The wall lamp is white and clean, just like a snow sculpture.

Name: Winter Bed
Desc: A very warm and cozy wooden bed. The blanket is made from self-heating fiber.

Name: Snowy Night Window
Desc: Outside the chilling window is the quiet snow.

Name: Winter Hunting
Desc: The trophy from a hunting trip.

Name: Throne of Redemption
Desc: Once Amberia's seat, it is filled with prayers and confessions.

Name: Laughing Attic
Desc: The pumpkin lamps light up the European style attic structure, make a laughing sound in the wind.

Name: Astrology Tiles
Desc: These ordinary-looking checkered tiles seem to contain some secret underneath.

Name: Astrology Curtain
Desc: The wall has the night view of city printed on it, resembling the look of a curtain.

Name: Sweet Shelf
Desc: This shelf is full of candies and gift boxes, leaving the most important astrology books all at the bottom.

Name: Astrology Table
Desc: A round table full of books and ritual tools. The candles are secured to the table, so feel free to shake it.

Name: Astrology Coffee Table
Desc: This coffee table seems to be regularly cleaned. Books are nicely placed on top, with a long black hair in between.

Name: Astrology Sofa
Desc: The cushions on this European style sofa are so soft that anyone who sits or lies on top will never feel like getting up again.

Name: Astrology Chair
Desc: This small chair can significantly ease the fatigue from extensive sitting during fortune-telling.

Name: Bed Curtain
Desc: Put down the curtains when you sleep on this dreamy European style bed.

Name: Mysterious Pot
Desc: This pot is making a strange-colored gas. Better not put your hand in it.

Name: Astrology Screen
Desc: A very mysterious screen with stars and magic circle on it.

Name: Astrology Carpet
Desc: The magic circle on this carpet keeps shining. It seems to bring back your dreams.

Name: Astrology Candlestick
Desc: Are you ready to listen to the candlestick's secret?

Name: Carnival Stand
Desc: A display stand often seen in festivals. Someone took it inside the room.

Name: Candy Wallpaper
Desc: A quite special coating process is adopted to make sweet smell appears vividly.

Name: Candy Floor
Desc: The subtle diamond lattice decorations spell out the look of a dream beast that roams in this sweet space.

Name: Candy Flag
Desc: Both flags and sweet smells converge here, then the next step is to turn the street into a dream platform as well.

Name: Bakery Booth
Desc: Recalling the back of the decorator I looked at when I was a child, it seems that...I would like to have another piece now.

Name: Mousse Table
Desc: You won't get fat for it can't be eaten at all. Well , I mean, just sit at it—it's a table.

Name: Macaron Stools
Desc: Is it the busiest time of the dessert store? Just sit down and gawk at somewhere... nearly forget the time.

Name: Dreamy Narwhal
Desc: Warmth is a beautiful dream that starts from a distant fairy tale. Give up resistance and indulge in dreams for a while.

Name: Dreamy Projector
Desc: Please rest assured that this product will not play your dream faithfully.

Name: Pocky Divider
Desc: It will not melt at room temperature, so please do not break it.

Name: Candy Pot
Desc: A little green accent often brings unexpected effects and freshness!

Name: Dark Choco
Desc: A, Anubis...In fact, this design should have another meaning, and can be regarded as a unique ornament

Name: Sweet Production
Desc: It makes me happy in—stantly! The tester said.

Name: Twirling Donut
Desc: The dessert will not fall even if you stare at it. Please take it yourself!

Name: Dreamy Crystal
Desc: Innocent and fantastic. Try to look at it from different angles, and there will be different refractions. Colors overlap and fall into dreams.

Name: Candy Window
Desc: Candy, chocolate, fragrance escapes from time to time. The window of dreams is nothing more than that.

Name: Candy Board
Desc: Too cute decoration makes no one able to touch it, and the entertainment role that should have been played has become a decorative role.

Name: Macaron Stool (Green)
Desc: Just like a meringue with skirt, it's a soft stool with first-class touch.

Name: Macaron Stool (Purple)
Desc: Just like a meringue with skirt, it's a soft stool with first-class touch.

Name: Macaron Stool (Yellow)
Desc: Just like a meringue with skirt, it's a soft stool with first-class touch.

Name: Theater Wall
Desc: This simplistic wall has no striking design, but it can play some Golden Age theater if the correct commands are entered.

Name: Theater Carpet
Desc: A hard, sound-absorbing carpet prepared for the audience who arrive late.

Name: Theater Crossbeam
Desc: Rumor has it that if a button is pressed, smoke would come out from the paper umbrellas that hang on the beam.

Name: Theater Bed
Desc: A very traditional frame bed. The mattress is a bit hard, but it really calms people down.

Name: Floor Lamp
Desc: This long-lasting lamp can be placed anywhere. It gives a warm light that mimics the sun.

Name: Bamboo Screen
Desc: This screen has a bamboo painting on it and seems to give a fresh fragrance whenever someone walks close.

Name: Theater Lamp
Desc: This soft-light lamp would automatically light up whenever someone enters the room.

Name: Theater Drum
Desc: Despite its enormous size, this drum makes the same sound no matter how hard people beat on it.

Name: Theater Stage
Desc: A simple classic wooden stage. There is no special effect like holographic technology, but it is open for anyone to go up and perform.

Name: Cloud Stand
Desc: This stand is for decorative purposes only, but people always mistake it for a cloth hanger.

Name: Snowy Blossoms
Desc: A painting of plum blossoms. According to the advertisement, the petals could change their form with the temperature, but no one has ever witnessed it.

Name: Theater Bookshelf
Desc: This tall "bookshelf" contains no electronic books, but "real" books made according to the data left from the Golden Age.

Name: Theater Window
Desc: Comes in a set of three, these windows are not very transparent.

Name: Theater Lounge
Desc: A soft lounge that also comes with a pillow. Sometimes used as a bed, it is in fact modified to be more comfortable than a bed.

Name: Theater Chair
Desc: A small chair with armrests. Whoever tries to squat on it would be seriously scolded.

Name: Theater Desk
Desc: A low desk made for playing music or painting on it.

Name: Timber Block
Desc: Made from thin wooden planks that are nicely assembled together. The pattern gives a solid and comfort feel.

Name: Stone Castle
Desc: This wall gives a solitary feel and somehow keeps people away.

Name: Skylight Ceiling
Desc: An archway with light coming from above. The light is artificial though — please keep this a secret.

Name: Greenery Swing
Desc: Sit on this chair and lose yourself in the green plants while swinging.

Name: Sugary Dream
Desc: One can hardly get away from this comfortable cocoon made from down and foam during wintertime.

Name: Magical Cabinet
Desc: Who left the cakes on this bakery cabinet?

Name: Tea Table
Desc: A small, round table with a velvet cover and freshly prepared desserts on top.

Name: Cocoa Chair
Desc: A very solid chair. Nobody knows why it smells like chocolate though...

Name: Tree Stump
Desc: A very old tree stump. Weird mushrooms have grown on it.

Name: Afternoon Leisure
Desc: There are pots and desserts on this trolley. "Auntie Witch" may have put more goodies...

Name: Forest Path
Desc: An incomplete painting portraying a forest path. The wet paint gives a fascinating smell.

Name: Fondant Fence
Desc: This white fence wraps around well-trimmed plants, but gives a sweet scent for no reason...

Name: Sweet Fragrance
Desc: The potted flowers smell so delicious. Wait a sec...Are they really flowers?

Name: Flower Stand
Desc: The plants on this flower stand never seem to wither.

Name: White Pillar
Desc: Crafted from polished white stone, this pillar has a small pot on its top.

Name: Wall Planter
Desc: A wall-hanging planter decorated with flowers and greenery. Also gives an amazing scent.

Name: Stained Glass
Desc: Made from rainbow-colored glass, this window gives colors to any light that shines through it.

Name: Falling Star Ceiling
Desc: The ceiling full of falling stars. As if we were in space, watched over by stars at night while dawn would still rise.

Name: Sleeping Pod
Desc: The soundproof sleeping pod allows the Construct resting inside to recover quickly.

Name: Star Patterned Bed
Desc: A neat bed. The bedding is decorated with star patterns, and lying in it is like falling into the embrace of the Milky Way.

Name: Weapon Locker
Desc: A locker that stores weapons. Dusted and cleaned, all weapons inside are properly maintained.

Name: Multipurpose Tactics Table
Desc: A table of coming up with tactics. The holo-screen projects an unfinished game of chess, the players of which are unknown.

Name: Cleaning Expert
Desc: An all-purpose cleaning robot, seemingly the latest model. Who put it in the room?

Name: Astronomical Telescope
Desc: An astronomical telescope developed by the Science Council. Find the right angle and through which you can see the Earth today.

Name: Starry Wall Lamp
Desc: A wall lamp decorated with hanging stars. When wind blows into the room, the stars will twinkle with the wind.

Name: Moonlit Window
Desc: A window on the wall. Through it, you can see a brilliant starry sky, which reminds you of a great painting in the Golden Age.

Name: Tactics Wall
Desc: A wall with the Strike Hawk logo, simple and solid. A furniture piece that only belongs to Strike Hawk.

Name: Lab White Wall
Desc: A wall that mimics the texture of the wall in the lab. It seems to be carrying a blank memory.

Name: Kowloong Bed
Desc: A piece of traditional Kowloong furniture. It's an antique-style bed that is comfortable to sleep on. You can even read ancient bamboo books on it if you like.

Name: Simulated Military Sleeping Pod
Desc: A sleeping pod created by some Babylonia enthusiasts. It's overall very similar to the original one and has even received the recognition of some Forsaken members.

Name: Standard Military Sleeping Pod
Desc: A small but comfortable military sleeping pod that is commonly used among the Forsaken members. It can be moved around in the control cabin if necessary.

Name: Sofa Bed
Desc: A customized sofa with the Strike Hawk logo with a full bedding set. It can be used directly as a bed for sleep.

Name: Akdilek's Tool Cabinet
Desc: A tool cabinet with the Akdilek logo with a uniform and a set of repair tools.

Name: Drawing Desk
Desc: A desk for drawing. It has witnessed the birth of many popular Babylonia graphic visual artworks. You can only paint with your art tools on it as it does not have any electronic functions.

Name: Maintenance Station Type-X68
Desc: A maintenance station created by the Gray Raven. It is equipped with simple maintenance tools, blueprints, and lights.

Name: Maintenance Station Type-X69
Desc: A maintenance station specially prepared for the Gray Raven with a high-definition display and scanning function. It can provide real-time analysis of the operation of the machine under maintenance.

Name: Simple Cooking Bench
Desc: A cooking bench with the most basic kitchen utensils. It's okay to use but still not convenient enough.

Name: Standard Cooking Bench
Desc: A well-equipped cooking bench often seen with weird dishes on it.

Name: Advanced Cooking Bench
Desc: A fully equipped cooking bench. The food on it looks mouthwatering, but please taste it with professionals by your side.

Name: Wooden Dummy
Desc: A wooden dummy to practice martial arts. Some love to practice with it even when it's outside of the training period.

Name: Ordinary Dress
Desc: A basic, branded dress for summer. It brings out the grace of a girl with its simple design with a focus on details.

Name: Haute Couture Dress
Desc: An haute couture branded dress for fall. Its design combines boldness and modest luxury and brings out the beauty of a girl.

Name: Jellyfish Bowl
Desc: A fish bowl with jellyfish swimming among the corals in it. Who sent this lovely, pinky gift to the girl?

Name: Holographic Galaxy Model
Desc: A holographic generator that mimics the galaxy and allows you to hold the stars in your hand. You just can't move your eyes off the galactic halo it projects.

Name: Racing Moto
Desc: An old yet still fashionable-looking moto. It has been well-maintained, and some of its parts seem to have been modified.

Name: Polar Deadwood
Desc: A tree decorated with ARU lights that add some warmth to the cold, withered branches.

Name: Drinking Dispenser: Basic
Desc: A drinking dispenser with a small AI. It will move to the user in a dramatic way and serve drinks for them when needed.

Name: Drinking Dispenser: With Tray Table
Desc: An upgraded drinking dispenser. It can strike a cool pose like a game character while serving food and drinks for the user when necessary.

Name: Basic-type Video Game Machine
Desc: A basic-type video game machine that supports most video games. You can also equip it with a projector to use.

Name: Home-type Video Game Machine
Desc: A home-type video game machine with an extra large screen that can provide the user with an immersive gaming experience.

Name: STAR Drum Set
Desc: An extremely fashionable set of drums that make you want to raise the drumsticks and beat the drums the minute you sit before them.

Name: Snack Shelf
Desc: A small shelf filled with snacks of various unique flavors. You won't be able to take any more food if you finish all the snacks.

Name: Portable Phonograph
Desc: A mechanical pet in a unique style. The phonograph is now playing the grand opera that is popular in Babylonia lately.

Name: Purple Feathered Bow Rest
Desc: A simple bow rest that can be hung on the wall. It always gives off a solitary vibe.

Name: White Feathered Bow Rest
Desc: A unique bow rest that can be hung on the wall. It reminds you of some holy religious stories.

Name: Holographic Fireworks
Desc: A holographic display window that shows fireworks blooming in the night sky with loud sound effects and focus on the moment that fireworks bloom.

Name: Holographic FC Fireworks
Desc: A holographic display window that shows fireworks blooming in the night sky in great audio and visual details. You can even see ashes falling from the fireworks.

Name: Route Display Panel
Desc: A display panel that records the detailed schedule and missions of an outstanding Construct of the current month.

Name: Strike Hawk's Dispatching Display Panel
Desc: A rectangular display panel that records the assignment and progress of the tasks Strike Hawk has for the current month.

Name: Movie Poster
Desc: A slightly faded movie poster. It's hard to tell whether the colors are from the costume of the performer or someone's doodling.

Name: STAR Rock Drum Set
Desc: A super fashionable rock drum set for professionals. Mind that you could use up your energy playing it.

Name: Pigeon Cage Globe
Desc: A commonly seen statue in Star of Life that resembles a pigeon cage. It is created to commemorate a hero.

Name: Whale Song Phonograph
Desc: A mechanical pet with the appearance of a whale. Its classic yet innovative style makes people wonder what music it will play.

Name: Neon Lion
Desc: A neon light ornament that combines hologram technology and an abstraction style. It's said that its original design was inspired by an auspicious giant beast.

Name: Full of Power
Desc: A cabin removed from Nanami's prototype aircraft. It has been recycled and upgraded to a rest cabin. Have a nap in it and you will be full of power!

Name: Daily Practice
Desc: A movable storage cage filled with basketballs for practice. Each basketball is covered with sweat, the efforts spent unmistakable.

Name: Classroom Blackboard
Desc: A blackboard with the words "School Festival" on it. Everything written here is proof of youth.

Name: Air Purifier
Desc: A simple air purifier. The stuffy classroom is in need of freshening.

Name: Cardboard Boxes
Desc: Cardboard boxes that are stacked together. Labeled with different categories, they better not get in the way.

Name: Spare Supplies
Desc: A tray of spare supplies for the School Festival. Always have a backup! Let's make sure the Festival runs smoothly!

Name: Bunting Banners
Desc: Small triangular flags hanging on a string, it is a DIY decoration item made by everyone. Use them to make the School Festival more lively!

Name: Classroom Chair
Desc: Move the chairs together to make a temporary bed. The School Festival is almost here! All spare time is spent on the preparation. Sleep on the chairs if you are tired!

Name: Classroom Table
Desc: Steady, durable classroom tables. Its wooden surface has recorded countless marks of youth.

Name: Wooden Floor
Desc: Beautiful wooden floor. Running or jumping wouldn't make a dent on it.

Name: Janitor's Lockers
Desc: A locker that keeps all the cleaning supplies. Labor is honorable, even if it is just cleaning.

Name: Basketball Hoop
Desc: A simple basketball hoop. You're running out of time—don't throw away your shot! Everyone has their eyes on you. The ball goes through the hoop with a "whoosh." With the sound of the whistle, the game is over.

Name: Running Track
Desc: Long, straight rubber tracks. Don't leave behind regrets—run! Give it everything you have. Run!

Name: Scoreboard
Desc: A scoreboard that marks the points. The score might be behind, but there is still a chance as long as the match hasn't ended!

Name: Snack Table
Desc: A table filled with snacks and drinks. Intensive sports have left everyone hungry, so grab some food here!

Name: Summerfest Stage
Desc: A stage with the spirit of summer. Everyone has helped build and decorate it, so take a photo here!

Name: Vault Sofa
Desc: A sofa in the shape of a vault. An apparatus for vaulting, it is also a good chair when you get tired.

Name: Colorful Wallpaper
Desc: Cover the white classroom walls with colorful wallpapers. Don't soil them!

Name: Water Cooler
Desc: A water cooler for when you are thirsty. Grab a cup of water instead of a soda here after doing sports.

Name: Classroom Window
Desc: Glass window that lets in sunlight. It might be a bit too bright during summer, but bathing in sunlight feels very comfortable.

Name: Milky Way Bridge
Desc: A bridge with a magpie paint on it. It's said that the bridge goes across 16.4 light years of the Milky Way... But of course the actual bridge is not longer than 16.4m.

Name: Cloud Beam
Desc: A beam with cloud totems. The clouds on the beam seem to be changing when the breeze passes through.

Name: Moondew Lantern
Desc: A floor lamp with dim light. Hope it can guide people to their true love.

Name: Magpie Window
Desc: A paper window with magpie patterns. One could hear the sound of the night breeze and the chirps of the magpies when standing close to it.

Name: Lotus Cake Stool
Desc: A lotus-Cake-shaped stool, which makes you want to have something sweet while sitting on it.

Name: Cream Cake Stool
Desc: A soft cream-Cake-slice-shaped stool, which makes you feel like sinking into it when sitting on it.

Name: Ice-cream Cake Stool
Desc: An ice-cream-Cake-slice-shaped stool, which makes you feel a bit cold when sitting on it.

Name: Green Bean Cake Stool
Desc: A green-bean-Cake-shaped stool, which puts you in a good mood when sitting on it.

Name: Five Nuts Cake Stool
Desc: A five-nuts-Cake-shaped stool, which gives you a mixed feeling when sitting on it.

Name: Cake Table
Desc: A Cake-shaped round table, which is suitable for family and friends to sit at it and enjoy the time together.

Name: Simple Medical Trolley
Desc: A simple trolley carrying medical devices, which is capable of supporting patients lives in emergencies.

Name: Common Physiotherapy Bed
Desc: The most common Star of Life physiotherapy bed equipped with a shadowless lamp and a simple analysis device, which can be used for some surgeries.

Name: Medic Sleeping Chamber
Desc: A mass-produced sleeping pod that combines comfort and functionality, which makes the user to fall asleep quickly regardless of their state of health.

Name: Cellular Structure Rings
Desc: A common ceiling ornament in Star of Life. The three linked rings remind people of the base unit of the life — the cell.

Name: Star Tower of Life
Desc: A Star of Life ornament, which shows how Star of Life headquarters is supposed to be like on Earth in the plan made in the Golden Age.

Name: Surgical Record Screen
Desc: A huge operating room screen that allows the medics to plan for surgeries and people assignment.

Name: Doctor's Office Desk
Desc: A common office desk for doctors to check case history, search information, and make diagnoses. However, there are a lot of complaints about not being able to find a pen for note-taking in the desk.

Name: Cultivation Square
Desc: A piece of floor with the Star of Life logo, a logo that has witnessed the maintenance and growth of numerous lives.

Name: Beehive Table
Desc: A set consists of a hexagonal table and a chair. Users can purchase multiple ones and put them together to be an organized secondary test bench.

Name: Indicator Screen
Desc: A holographic originally designed to direct patients. It can also be used as a simple display screen and set to a default display mode in the dormitory.

Name: Robotic Arm with Screen
Desc: A robotic arm that can move equipment and medicines around while accessing their data to avoid leaving objects behind.

Name: Beehive Stand
Desc: A ornament stand commonly seen in the hall of Star of Life, which combines a good texture and a sense of technology.

Name: Double-Deck Cart
Desc: A cart that carries medicines and potions, which is commonly seen in pharmacies.

Name: Star of Life Sofa Bed
Desc: A sofa bed commonly see in doctor's offices. It was originally designed for medics to take a nap, but they rarely have the time for it.

Name: Case History Terminal
Desc: A terminal used to store patient data including case history, allergies, etc., which can be turned on with medic ID cards.

Name: Wall of Prayers
Desc: A wall decoration occasionally seen in Star of Life. The walls in hospitals have listened to more sincere prayers than those in churches.

Name: Winged Snake Scepter
Desc: A common ornament in Star of Life. Its design was inspired by the snake scepter symbolizing resurrection and rebirth in mythology.

Name: Physiotherapy Chair
Desc: A physiotherapy chair used to diagnose and treat patients with chronic and mild diseases. There is also a more common household version.

Name: Stained Glass Window
Desc: A window made with stained glass, which was commonly seen on religious buildings but now widely used in decoration.

Name: Kuroro Bar Counter
Desc: A bar counter with various tools. Kuroro always plays bartender and shakes the shot glass behind the counter, but actually what's in it is milk.

Name: Disco Ball
Desc: Steel frames with lights and a disco ball that helps to create a perfect stage.

Name: Kuroro Sticker
Desc: Just a Kuroro wall sticker. The Kuroro on it is definitely not staring at you. Definitely not.

Name: DJ Booth
Desc: Mixing, shifting sounds, dropping sound effects... Whoever stands behind it will surely be busy, but Kuroro can handle anything!

Name: Clang-Clang Electronic Drum Set
Desc: The most common electronic drum set in discos. There is no way to create a clang-clang sound with it, but that's just how Kuroro named it.

Name: Super High Dancing Floor
Desc: An exciting dance floor device that will shine when you step on any of the color blocks in the center.

Name: Tuner Electric Guitar
Desc: It looks like an ordinary electric guitar, but its stand is actually a tuner connected to the guitar. Those who don't know how to play guitar can still satisfy themselves with it.

Name: Distortion Microphone
Desc: A microphone that can distort your voice in various ways. The fan mode is the most popular mode.

Name: Disco Sofa
Desc: A leather disco sofa. It's said that its original design has the function of massaging the user based on the volume of the sound in the environment. Unfortunately, the function is not included in the final design.

Name: Shining Stage
Desc: A stage with amazing visual effects, which can make anyone standing on it look like a superstar.

Name: Stereo Speaker
Desc: A floorstanding speaker with perfect sound quality able to project sound to every corner. Somehow it also has the music note visual effect just like the speaker in manga.

Name: Disco Stool
Desc: A disco stool. The circles on it are actually part of a trampoline.

Name: Volume Table
Desc: A table that visualizes the music volume with patterns changing with the volume!——It's said that the table is designed based on this concept.

Name: Music Wave Wall
Desc: A wall that turns music into visual art. The moving patterns make people can't help but wag their heads in time to the music.

Name: Kuroro Display Case
Desc: A display case placed in the most prominent spot. The bottles in it all have the Kuroro logo on them. Is the case too tall for the user? Well, there's no need to worry about that.

Name: Score Monster
Desc: It's a good idea to play darts in your spare time as long as you don't get mad when you score low.

Name: Throne
Desc: A single-seater leather sofa in a unique color. It goes without saying how important the person who sits on it is.

Name: Godfather's Coat Rack
Desc: A wooden coat tree that is stable, elegant, low-key, yet luxurious.

Name: Areca Palm
Desc: A lush plant with big leaves. It's said that it brings good luck to your career.

Name: Kingpin's Round Table
Desc: A round table temporarily used for work. It comes with all the office items you can imagine.

Name: Spring Scenery Window
Desc: A well-designed window with branches seeming to stick out from it.

Name: Marble Stool
Desc: A delicate stool carved out from an entire rock. It feels a bit cold to sit on it.

Name: Rockery Ornament
Desc: A stone floor ornament It looks like the miniature of a famous mountain.

Name: Stone Go Board
Desc: A bluestone table with a tea set and a go board. You can spend most of your day sitting at it.

Name: Greeting Pine
Desc: An evergreen plant ornament. Its branches seem to be greeting the guests.

Name: Mosaic Floor
Desc: When technology turns fineness into crudeness, the past has also been recorded.

Name: Green Grating
Desc: A lively grating, through which one could see the world in the deep alley.

Name: Colorful Ceiling
Desc: You will forget about your worries just by hearing the names of delicacies.

Name: Moment of Respite
Desc: A simple, spacious design for a free and comfy space.

Name: Good Sleep Rocking Chair
Desc: Move backward and forward and you will fall into a nice sleep.

Name: Vending Machine Closet
Desc: You can find everything from soda water to vital fluid in it. Just make sure you don't pick the wrong one.

Name: Square Restaurant Table
Desc: A square table with a menu between the glass and the tabletop. Its big size always makes the "standard menu" looks small on it.

Name: Round Restaurant Table
Desc: A round table with a menu between the glass and the tabletop. Its small size makes it convenient to order with the "standard menu."

Name: Restaurant Folding Chair
Desc: A simple space-saving folding chair with multiple usages.

Name: Beverage Box
Desc: These simple boxes are easy to be piled up and can be opened anywhere to serve drinks.

Name: Dining Car
Desc: An all-weather general-purpose vehicle that can be used on all kinds of occasions, especially good at missions in downtown areas. It is filled with popular delicacies.

Name: Chinese Lantern
Desc: One part of it was made by the passage of time, and the other part of it was made of iron.

Name: Plastic Stool
Desc: When piled together, these plastic stools will become stronger than expected. Combine them with wood boards to set up a table for temporary use.

Name: Traffic Light
Desc: You might be able to find delicacies following the light... Anyways, you won't walk to the outside.

Name: Red Envelope Citrus Tree
Desc: A citrus tree that carries good wishes.

Name: Firecrackers Decoration
Desc: It's a decoration that can't be ignited. However, people still believe it can chase away bad luck.

Name: Chinese Character Decoration
Desc: A lucky charm that can be stuck to a wall. Such decorations have been disappearing over time.

Name: Nostalgic Screen
Desc: A simple, unique, nostalgic screen that divides a room.

Name: Retro Screens
Desc: Not fashionable, nor ancient, they just stand there with other old items, creating a special style.

Name: Knight's Dream
Desc: Soft and comfy, it is also the portal to the dragon's life mission.

Name: Precious Collection
Desc: The books are precious, but so is the old bookshelf that passed down through generations.

Name: Smart Brain
Desc: A table with piles of research materials. A knight should be armed with more than just a sword and an armor.

Name: Symbol of Lordship
Desc: With its high back showing lordship power, the chair provides a moment of rest for its user.

Name: Weapons of Glory
Desc: A sword and a shield of glory. Perhaps this combination will release miraculous power.

Name: Nature's Embrace
Desc: Fall asleep in this carefully made tent hammock and the company of nature.

Name: Fruits and Veggies
Desc: Freshly picked fruits and veggies are placed on a cart, making it possible for them to appear on your stove no matter where it is.

Name: Minimalism
Desc: High-end minimalism usually consists of the simplest materials. For example, several ropes and some wood.

Name: Lawn Stool
Desc: A stool inspired by lawn. It looks like a piece of lawn uprooted from the ground and planted in a wooden basin.

Name: Fruit and Veggie Pool
Desc: Let the fruits and veggies wash themselves clean while swimming for the last time.

Name: Fluffy Haicma
Desc: A fluffy plush toy designed based on Haicma. Nanami insists that it should be smiling.

Name: Glorious Days
Desc: Excitement, happiness, and sadness... She let herself indulge in the emotions, walking slowly down memory lane. It ends playing. The coordinates of the future are still in the distance. She has to put them away in her heart and set off again.

Name: Tea Party Table
Desc: A carefully arranged long table. It indicates that a special tea party is about to begin.

Name: Dessert Party
Desc: A delicious aroma comes from the various baked desserts on the table.

Name: Tea Time
Desc: A comfortable armchair that will put you in an elegant and relaxing posture.

Name: Mr. Bunny
Desc: Mr. Bunny hugs the potted plant he cares for each day, creating a dreamlike atmosphere for tea parties.

Name: Wonderland Invitation
Desc: A board with "Tea Time" written on it. When does the tea party start?

Name: Fantasy World
Desc: A fence entwined with morning glory and green vines. Entering is like stepping into a dream.

Name: Truther Seeker Sofa
Desc: A soft and comfy old-fashioned sofa. Taking a nap on it may bring inspiration.

Name: Thinking Chair
Desc: A wooden chair used by detectives. It's said to help one's concentration.

Name: Unveiling Desk
Desc: An antique desk containing many small items used by a detective hidden within.

Name: Deduction Table
Desc: A round table with a chessboard. An exquisite battle of the minds is about to commence.

Name: Inspiration Fireplace
Desc: A fireplace pulsing with orange flames. Gazing into it, you may see sparks of inspiration.

Name: Detective Board
Desc: A board full of clues and pictures. A spiderweb-like trail will eventually lead to the truth.

Name: Audiophile Cabinet
Desc: A display cabinet filled with CDs. Headphones fit for true audiophiles can block out the world to enjoy music to the fullest.

Name: Sea of Books Bookshelf
Desc: A bookshelf holding a large number of books. You can find all kinds of books in it.

Name: Warm Tea
Desc: A book and a cup of tea under the light. May this time of peace last forever.

Name: Cotton Cushion Chair
Desc: The soft cushion makes you don't want to stand up once you sit on it.

Name: Trolley
Desc: A trolley used to transport items. It's full of books now.

Name: Universe Gaze
Desc: A telescope for observing the starry sky.

Name: Tea Cabinet
Desc: Good tea needs no bush. Boil a pot of good tea and enjoy a happy family time.

Name: Flowing Stream
Desc: A long table inspired by streams, full of traditional festive foods.

Name: Hollyhock Chair
Desc: A traditional low chair, whose cushion has a faint scent.

Name: Rice's Aroma Stove
Desc: A stove that burns firewood as fuel. It's said that the rice you cook with firewood yourself is especially tasty.

Name: Pouring Greenness
Desc: A green willow leaf ornament. Looks cute when blowing in the wind.

Name: Grass Ornament
Desc: An ornament made of grass. It symbolizes the virtue of human beings.

Name: Firefly Memory
Desc: The firefly that only stays here. The lonely, comfortable swing. The evergreen vines... To him, these are the memory, the present, and the future.

Name: Classic Style
Desc: A classic-style floor tile.

Name: Sunset Electric Wave
Desc: A wall with an electronic screen. The sunset pattern on it is very popular among customers.

Name: Neon Sky
Desc: A ceiling with spotlights. It seems that the color of the lights can change with the music.

Name: Locomotive Sofa
Desc: A sofa modified from a locomotive. It's surprisingly comfortable.

Name: Car Back Sofa
Desc: A sofa modified from a car back. It has a strange structure but is surprisingly stable.

Name: Car Bed
Desc: A bed modified from a chassis. You can take a nap on it when you're tired.

Name: Old Style Freezer
Desc: A freezer filled with alcohols. The bartenders' performance is the biggest selling point of the restaurant.

Name: Vendor Machine GOGO
Desc: A vender machine filled with cold drinks. You could get another drink for free if you're lucky enough.

Name: Nostalgia
Desc: A dinner table with an old BCL receiver that contains hundreds of classic radio show recordings from the Golden Age.

Name: Restaurant Chair
Desc: A simple restaurant chair, sturdy and durable.

Name: Hit Song
Desc: A music cabinet that creates atmosphere for the restaurant. It will keep playing the classic pop music of the present century during the opening hours.

Name: Four-Stroke Bar Counter
Desc: It's said that it is a bar counter modified from a real car engine, but it can't quadruple the staff's work efficiency.

Name: Dusk
Desc: Let the time stop at this moment and make the sunset eternal.

Name: This Way Please
Desc: The sign means, "This way please."

Name: Sunset Light
Desc: A light board made with numerous light bulbs. The light golden light is just like the lingering light of the setting sun.

Name: Golden Age
Desc: The frame holds a memory that one will cherish forever.

Name: Starless Night
Desc: She will guard your dream even in the darkest starless night.

Name: クロロトーテムポール
Desc: 世界政府芸術協会が発掘した遺物。古代の人類はこれをある種のシンボルや祈祷に用いた

Name: クロロオペラハウス
Desc: 地球上の某所に存在する帆船や貝殻を模した歌劇場…のはずだが何か別の要素が混ざっているようだ。

Name: クロロ·イッツァ
Desc: 地球上の某古代文明の遺跡を模した置物。不思議なトーテムのホログラムが浮かび上がる。

Name: 真珠の耳飾りのセリカ
Desc: 黄金時代よりさらに昔の有名画家の作品。耳飾りをつけた少女が描かれている。

Name: セリカの微笑
Desc: 奥深く謎めいた絵画。空中庭園で最も美しい作品と言われている（WARNING：この記述は改ざんの形跡が検出されました）

Name: Kuroro Thunder Gate
Desc: Designed based on a famous tourism spot on the earth, there is a huge red Kuroro lantern hanging in the middle.

Name: Kuroro Totem
Desc: It is found that humans in ancient times built such totems as serve to symbols and blessings, according to a research from the Association of Art.

Name: Kuroro Opera House
Desc: A sail-shaped theater building on the earth. But for some reason, there seems to be a Kuroro standing there.

Name: Kuroro Temple
Desc: A model based on a temple building on Earth.

Name: Kuroro Needle
Desc: A model based on a landmark building on Earth.

Name: Great Kuroro Sphinx
Desc: A golden model made according to historical and archaeological records, but its face looks a bit familiar…

Name: Big Kuroro
Desc: Ding-dong, ding-dong. Kuroro chimes for you.

Name: Kuroro City Ruins
Desc: An ornament made in accordance with an archeological site on Earth. A mysterious image will be projected on it.

Name: Celica with Pearl Earrings
Desc: The painting depicts a woman wearing a pearl earring.

Name: Mona Celica
Desc: It can be called the most beautiful painting of E-02 'Babylonia' so far. (Warning! The description data has been maliciously modified)
